{"tid":273163,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"excel問題 if or and公式求救","createTime":"2017-06-06T10:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T07:17:33.000Z","uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2bf1adc9f82a0d3e75df2ee04ebe593c807cfeba","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:57:47.000Z","msg":"假設我要分獎金比啲學生 但要睇埋佢排名同成績應該點計？<br />\n例子：<br />\n排名20或以內 <br />\n成績A+,A,A-  =可以獲得800蚊獎<br />\n成績B+,B,B-  =可以獲得600蚊<br />\n成績C+,C,C- =可以獲得500蚊<br />\n<br />\n排名20-30<br />\n成績A+,A,A-  =可以獲得300蚊獎<br />\n成績B+,B,B-  =可以獲得200蚊<br />\n成績C+,C,C- =可以獲得100蚊<br />\n<br />\n排名30-40<br />\n成績A+,A,A-  =可以獲得50蚊獎<br />\n成績B+,B,B-  =可以獲得20蚊<br />\n成績C+,C,C- =可以獲得10蚊<br />\n<br />\n成績係D以下 或者41名以上就無獎分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞左好耐都寫唔到出黎 有冇巴打可以救下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be43ec7ce0b85f003e13adc8eac6cc9e8ef280c","tid":273163,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:00:54.000Z","msg":"開另一個column擺排名先"},{"pid":"62ab05f090f1b793c817107c0dd7c601424e9982","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046fdd736613027aaf2a33c925982f05ea28dff5","tid":273163,"uid":34202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:03:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\nyes 跟住lookup名次 再lookup grade"},{"pid":"1b7b3dbf55d65bcfd65b7e365954734ad346a0ff","tid":273163,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:04:26.000Z","msg":"加一列用countif set 條件，用1,2,3,4... 代替每一個條件，再用 sumif 加埋佢"},{"pid":"9fec11ea0871918ae1f75c4384d0ee0ccdabdc4b","tid":273163,"uid":50310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:11:02.000Z","msg":"唔鍾意用if丫！功課自己做<br />\n<br />\n整個sheetB獨立表：<br />\n01A  800<br />\n01A- 800<br />\n01A+ 800<br />\n...<br />\n40C+ 10<br />\n<br />\n然後<br />\n=vlookup(a2&amp;b2, sheetB!$A:$B, 2, false)"},{"pid":"6a507fa3a557b6b3cda857d92f9ac8b766505a9a","tid":273163,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:11:07.000Z","msg":"如果你開嘅Column愈多<br />\n你條formula就愈簡單<br />\n例如你可以開多個column, 顯示佢個grade係A, B, C定D<br />\n咁你就可以省返好多個OR，條formula短啲你就易睇啲<br />\n<br />\n如果可以用vba就更加簡單。"},{"pid":"68390710b0933f952403a5cb14db71c4cefb7135","tid":273163,"uid":117454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"你本身個TABLE係點放D DATA嫁??<br />\n比個圖黎睇睇"},{"pid":"3458861a413b3eb3c06a67267092dcbf13f9724e","tid":273163,"uid":88601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"首先將A+,A,A-全部當成A<br />\n然後用最直接公式<br />\n=IF((AND(E3&lt;21,F3=&quot;A&quot;)),800,IF((AND(E3&lt;21,F3=&quot;B&quot;)),600,IF((AND(E3&lt;21,F3=&quot;C&quot;)),500,IF((AND(E3&lt;31,F3=&quot;A&quot;)),300,IF((AND(E3&lt;31,F3=&quot;B&quot;)),200,IF((AND(E3&lt;31,F3=&quot;C&quot;)),100,IF((AND(E3&lt;41,F3=&quot;A&quot;)),50,IF((AND(E3&lt;41,F3=&quot;B&quot;)),20,IF((AND(E3&lt;41,F3=&quot;C&quot;)),10,0)))))))))"},{"pid":"b780346e668ec09603ffb67ca4c0bde69959a1d6","tid":273163,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))"},{"pid":"acc6df9e65b23607951c09c63166f6a72792a01d","tid":273163,"uid":117454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:25:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你個TABLE係咁先, <br />\n你要好多個IF先得<br />\n=if(and(排名&lt;=20,Left(GRADE,1)=&quot;A&quot;),$,if(and(排名&lt;=20,Left(GRADE,1)=&quot;B&quot;),$,if(and(排名&lt;=20,Left(GRADE,1)=&quot;C&quot;),$,if(and(排名&gt;20,排名&lt;=30,Left(GRADE,1)=&quot;A&quot;),$,if(...............,0)))))))))"},{"pid":"1d03fb195ec4d2cb6965baf1110833bea6b71f53","tid":273163,"uid":88601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:25:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LEFT(F3,1)即係咩"},{"pid":"a3a144a3efec40693e0fd18d74e61fb8bc6ae600","tid":273163,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LEFT(F3,1)即係咩</blockquote><br />\n成績有分A+, A, A-三種<br />\n但我們淨係睇佢係咪A range就夠<br />\nLeft(F3,1)可以忽略咗+同-，淨係睇字頭係A, B定C"},{"pid":"5e7c7c79db160d50dca28803948fb035b1d18441","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))</blockquote><br />\n唔該哂巴打 但我收左工 聽朝返去試試！<br />\n感激不盡！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0d0cbbee742617339b2c2bf6a75694168237ba","tid":273163,"uid":106422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LEFT(F3,1)即係咩</blockquote><br />\n要F3格左邊第一個字<br />\n由於你ABC正定負唔影響獎金，所以分左個ABC出黎縮短條式"},{"pid":"f8f01b0a43c8989fbc48629db6ed465cd51d5749","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加一列用countif set 條件，用1,2,3,4... 代替每一個條件，再用 sumif 加埋佢</blockquote><br />\n學到野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該哂各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a343878099fca4150158a3e595a1d5ab9a18b1","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:35:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開另一個column擺排名先</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/06/190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F06%2F190306_cc3e4988cd0f8a02f12531a1d646a75f.jpg&h=fd6fc51b&s={SIZE}\" />一開始就卡住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我試試先巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫你寫咗<br />\n你在G3貼依條formula試下<br />\n=IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;A&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,800,IF(E3&lt;=30,300,IF(E3&lt;=40,50,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;B&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,600,IF(E3&lt;=30,200,IF(E3&lt;=40,20,0))),IF(LEFT(F3,1)=&quot;C&quot;,IF(E3&lt;=20,500,IF(E3&lt;=30,100,IF(E3&lt;=40,10,0))),0)))</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> LEFT(F3,1)即係咩</blockquote><br />\n要F3格左邊第一個字<br />\n由於你ABC正定負唔影響獎金，所以分左個ABC出黎縮短條式</blockquote><br />\n原來可以咁 學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c7606ba7f8818627a81c5898228d32d9459e72","tid":273163,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:36:38.000Z","msg":"中學功課?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588f086e1709caec2d8e03752d6d854dc9ed5df6","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:37:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你本身個TABLE係點放D DATA嫁??<br />\n比個圖黎睇睇</blockquote><br />\n類似上面張圖咁 <br />\n啲資料貼上黎驚比人告 唔放得 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5beead6c7f103e9372948a9f281c17eccc6b0489","tid":273163,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"再次感激各巴打 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da7d007cc36f331cad49b6a7dc15a1fdef8238be","tid":273163,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T12:44:58.000Z","msg":"中五ict功課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03debb9e7e7a64e81eda0e965a40ede38821b9a","tid":273163,"uid":62932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T16:37:00.000Z","msg":"H1 = 4-IF(F1&lt;21,1)-IF(F1&lt;31,1)-IF(F1&lt;41,1)&amp;LEFT(G1)<br />\nI1 = VLOOKUP(H1,C$1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />$9,2,FALSE)<br />\n可以試下咁寫"},{"pid":"15cc645e7057a82172e1246bffe9f7506e14af61","tid":273163,"uid":62932